Vital Point to Capture?(2)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to play\b0 .
\par White's eye-space is not so big.
\par Actually it might be a very easy problem.
\par
\par However it is also important to be steady with the easy problems, then your basics are going to be good.
\par
\par The first move decides everything.
\par }
