Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's \cf1\b placement \cf0\b0 at 1 is a powerful vital point.
\par
\par It is also the 1-2 vital point.
\par If White plays at A, Black connects with B and White is dead.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
